      "condicoes": "The work will be performed at the Department of Informatics Engineering (DEI-FCTUC) and in collaboration with FiberSight (https://fibersight.pt/).\r\n\r\nIn FiberSight, the work will be supervised by:\r\n\r\n- PhD. Tiago Neves (tiago.neves@fibersight.pt)",
      "observacoes": "Additional resources:\r\n\r\n- Core Frameworks. Databricks or an open-source equivalent (Spark + Delta Lake) for the lakehouse implementation.\r\n- Orchestration. Apache Airflow or AWS Glue for managing complex fusion workflows.\r\n- Data Sources. FiberSight telemetry, Copernicus Open Access Hub for weather/satellite data, and public Smart City IoT datasets.\r\n",
