      "tem_juri": false,
      "add_aluno_pos_inicio_candidatura": false,
      "inicio_candidaturas": false,
      "condicoes": "The student will have access to all the computational resources necessary to carry out the work. A workspace at CISUC (Centre for Informatics and Systems of the University of Coimbra) will also be made available.\r\n\r\nThere is the possibility of funding in the ADSafeVANET project (task T2).",
